      "rationale": "The elastic-plastic isotropic hardening model for Ti-6Al-4V is justified by published tensile coupon data (Nagaraja et al. 2019) and is consistent with FDA-recognised material characterisation practice. The penalty contact formulation with μ = 0.2 is supported by prior spinal implant FEA literature. Both choices are documented in the simulation plan with supporting references. Gradation 2 is achieved."
