      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V material properties were sourced from tensile coupon testing of the same material lot used in the bench constructs (n=5 coupons; E = 114 ± 2 GPa, σ_y = 880 ± 12 MPa). Screw and rod geometry was taken from vendor-certified CAD files with a dimensional inspection report confirming < 0.05 mm deviation from nominal. All inputs are traceable and documented. Gradation 2 is achieved."
