      "rationale": "Construct stiffness is linked to the clinical failure mode of instrumentation loosening; yield force and force at 40 mm displacement are directly referenced in the FDA guidance for spinal system 510(k) submissions. All three QoIs are explicitly mapped to regulatory acceptance criteria in Section 3 of the credibility assessment report. Gradation 2 is achieved."
